00:01:26.080 --> 00:01:34.320
The prophet Nathan went and told David something very hard.

00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:38.159
But David was loved amongst the people.

00:01:38.159 --> 00:01:38.1000
Everybody loved David.

00:01:38.1000 --> 00:01:40.270
David was the man.

00:01:40.270 --> 00:01:44.743
But nobody knew what was going on behind closed doors.

00:01:44.743 --> 00:01:54.456
When the men were out to war, David was at home looking at naked women on the balcony, messing around and doing things.

00:01:54.456 --> 00:01:56.720
But it wasn't a popular thing.

00:01:56.720 --> 00:02:05.280
But Nathan pulled David aside privately and said, "This is what the Lord has to say to you.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:24.190
" And sometimes, out of what I believe the Lord gives me, are these words of warning, words of affirmation, words of correction that are not always easy to give.

00:02:26.290 --> 00:02:31.440
But Nathan did it, and it wasn't the easy thing to do because David was popular.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:32.709
David was loved.

00:02:32.709 --> 00:02:40.080
But nobody knew what was going on behind David's door when no one was looking.

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:42.937
And sometimes we can see people.

00:02:43.314 --> 00:02:45.609
I'm not accusing anybody of anything.

00:02:46.426 --> 00:02:49.359
I only hear in part, I see in part.

00:02:51.279 --> 00:03:10.560
