00:03:14.570 --> 00:03:29.519
" Then I say, just like Saul, Saul was a bad man, was killing Christians and was wrong, was awful, and the prophet didn't even want to go and pray for him after he went blind.

00:03:38.570 --> 00:03:39.000
He was scared for his life.

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:46.260
But the Lord said, "Go and pray for him and I'll restore his sight.

00:03:46.260 --> 00:03:48.810
" It wasn't an easy thing.

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:06.280
But he spoke and said, "This is what God said.

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:13.584
" But Paul, that was Saul, turned around and was one of the greatest voices of the Bible.

00:04:18.799 --> 00:04:19.089
