01:32:11.463 --> 01:32:13.400
We're not worried about how much we have.

01:32:31.440 --> 01:32:33.277
We just know that you're the God of multiplication.

01:32:39.719 --> 01:32:42.800
And I believe that whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap.

01:32:56.039 --> 01:32:57.480
And we thank you, Lord, that as tithers and givers, we believe that you said you'll give unto us good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over, Father, that we lack no good thing.

01:32:57.480 --> 01:33:00.576
We cover our sin in the blood, Lord.

01:33:00.848 --> 01:33:03.874
We cover our lives in the blood.

01:33:14.987 --> 01:33:15.253
And we thank you, Father, for the blood right now in the name of Jesus.

01:33:15.253 --> 01:33:25.387
And we thank you, Father, that we hear you and a stranger's voice will not follow, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:33:28.052 --> 01:33:31.520
Father, I thank you that you speak through my vocal cords and think through my mind.

01:33:31.520 --> 01:33:35.080
None of me and all of you, in Jesus' name.

01:33:45.413 --> 01:33:49.696
I thank you, Lord, that I don't get snared by anything and I hear you, God.

01:33:53.493 --> 01:33:55.883
And if there's anything you want to show us tonight as we pray, Father, we're there.

01:33:55.883 --> 01:33:57.430
If not, that's fine.

01:33:57.430 --> 01:33:58.818
We don't seek the visions.

01:33:58.818 --> 01:34:00.640
We don't seek the gift.

01:34:00.640 --> 01:34:04.285
We seek the giver of the gift.

01:34:22.620 --> 01:34:22.1000
We never have ever sought visions.

01:34:40.015 --> 01:34:40.191
We seek the giver.

01:34:58.080 --> 01:34:58.400
We seek you.

01:35:00.674 --> 01:35:02.091
We don't seek that, Father; that would be bad.

01:35:02.091 --> 01:35:04.400
But we seek you, Father.

01:35:21.893 --> 01:35:22.435
For Father, you said that you would inhabit the praises of your people, and you give us the desires of our heart.

01:35:42.754 --> 01:35:43.291
And our desire is to be more like you and to fall more in love with my friend because he is my friend.

01:35:49.840 --> 01:35:50.560
Thank you, Lord.

01:35:50.560 --> 01:35:52.960
We don't seek the gift.

01:36:10.949 --> 01:36:11.280
We don't seek visions.

01:36:11.280 --> 01:36:13.320
We don't seek the prophetic.

01:36:13.320 --> 01:36:16.100
We seek Jesus.

01:36:16.100 --> 01:36:17.931
We don't seek healings.

01:36:33.093 --> 01:36:33.440
We don't seek prosperity.

01:36:34.480 --> 01:36:34.827
We seek Jesus.

01:36:36.709 --> 01:36:37.006
We seek you, Lord.

01:36:37.006 --> 01:36:45.760
Father, in all that we do, in word and in deed, we give all to the glory of God.

01:36:46.050 --> 01:36:52.960
In all that we say and all that we do, we give all to the glory of God.

01:36:52.960 --> 01:36:59.005
And we take the blood right now in the name of Jesus.

01:36:59.005 --> 01:37:00.468
Thank you, Lord.

01:37:00.468 --> 01:37:03.760
It's relationship, and we want relationship with you.

01:37:20.377 --> 01:37:20.891
I want a God that I can talk to.

01:37:20.891 --> 01:37:24.617
I want him to be real to me.

01:37:25.211 --> 01:37:37.679
And when you get real with God, God will become real to you.

01:37:37.679 --> 01:37:47.768
So much fakeness, so much thee and thou, and so much hermeneutical and theosophical debating.

01:37:47.768 --> 01:37:51.889
He never said, 'I wanted you to be adults.

01:37:51.889 --> 01:37:56.879
' He said, 'Come unto me like children.

01:37:56.879 --> 01:38:00.034
' So many people try to come spiritual.

01:38:00.034 --> 01:38:16.880
'Well, I got a PhD and a masters and all this other stuff, and I'm telling you, I know the word and I am just like the Pharisees up in here.

01:38:16.880 --> 01:38:24.040
' But he's just going, 'Well, I ask you to be like a little kid.

01:38:24.040 --> 01:38:26.800
' It's good to educate yourself.

01:38:26.800 --> 01:38:55.600
It's good to have a knowledge of the word, but come to him as a child because your education and all that you think you know is really nothing.

01:38:55.600 --> 01:39:00.582
He's looking at you going, 'Your education's a joke to me.

01:39:00.582 --> 01:39:26.093
I'm glad you just studied to show yourself approved, but really you just need to lower your pride level down and know that you are just coming in here with your pampers on still before the Father.

01:39:26.093 --> 01:39:29.097
' Come before the Father with your pampers on.

01:39:29.097 --> 01:39:30.880
I just need daddy.

01:39:30.880 --> 01:39:32.680
Please fix this.

01:39:32.680 --> 01:39:39.979
I got a mess up in here that only you can fix.

01:39:54.468 --> 01:39:54.719
Lord, my life is a mess without you.

01:40:09.520 --> 01:40:09.720
Father, I need you, Jesus.

01:40:27.507 --> 01:40:28.080
All have sinned and come short of the glory of God.

01:40:33.040 --> 01:40:33.413
I don't care how much they try to put on a religious front.

01:40:51.320 --> 01:40:51.653
All have sinned and have come short of the glory of God.

01:40:51.653 --> 01:40:57.190
It's only by his grace that you're able to stay in that throne.

01:41:02.525 --> 01:41:06.090
Thank you, Lord, for the grace that Jesus paid the price for me to walk in victory over all of this.

01:41:06.090 --> 01:41:11.279
It's only by grace Jesus paid the price for me.

01:41:19.829 --> 01:41:29.199
And we confess it and we get rid of it and we keep walking with it.

01:41:29.199 --> 01:41:31.029
Thank you for your grace.

01:41:31.029 --> 01:41:32.960
Thank you for your mercy.

01:41:55.859 --> 01:41:56.189
Thank you, Father, for your relationship.

01:41:56.189 --> 01:41:57.510
I receive it.

01:41:57.510 --> 01:42:03.090
I am the righteousness of God in Christ Jesus.

01:42:03.090 --> 01:42:06.880
As he is, so am I in this world.

01:42:22.290 --> 01:42:22.740
It's all washed in the blood.

01:42:22.740 --> 01:42:25.973
Thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:42:25.973 --> 01:42:28.050
Thank you, Lord, for redeeming me.

01:42:49.760 --> 01:42:50.149
Thank you, Lord, for setting me free.

01:42:50.149 --> 01:42:58.296
Christ paid the price of the broken law.

01:42:58.296 --> 01:43:02.267
He paid the price for me.

01:43:02.267 --> 01:43:04.387
I'm not under the curse.

01:43:04.387 --> 01:43:07.040
Jesus has set me free.

01:43:16.959 --> 01:43:17.319
For sickness, I have health.

01:43:24.300 --> 01:43:24.910
For poverty, wealth, for Christ has ransomed me.

01:43:24.910 --> 01:43:30.489
He said, 'Not with one spot, one blemish or blot.

01:43:30.489 --> 01:43:33.649
' His blood was shed for me.

01:43:44.068 --> 01:43:44.445
Thank you, Lord, that Jesus Christ paid the price for me.

01:43:51.200 --> 01:43:53.520
And Lord, we thank you that we're able to enter in boldly by your blood, by your grace, by your mercy right now.

01:44:01.901 --> 01:44:02.239
We yield ourselves over to you.

01:44:02.239 --> 01:44:04.600
Open the eyes of our heart, Lord.

01:44:04.600 --> 01:44:07.066
Open the eyes of our heart.

01:44:07.066 --> 01:44:10.280
I want to see you.

01:44:12.182 --> 01:44:12.685
We worship you tonight, Lord.

01:44:29.920 --> 01:44:30.606
We worship you.

01:44:46.719 --> 01:44:46.959
We magnify your name in all the earth.

01:44:51.326 --> 01:44:51.623
We glorify your name in all the earth.

01:44:56.780 --> 01:44:57.040
Holy Spirit, we love you.

01:44:57.560 --> 01:44:58.080
We praise you.

01:45:01.679 --> 01:45:02.239
We adore you.

01:45:11.371 --> 01:45:11.703
We glorify your name in all the earth.

01:45:31.519 --> 01:45:31.759
Lord, we praise you.

01:45:38.159 --> 01:45:40.240
We worship you, for you are good and your mercy endures forever.

01:45:45.062 --> 01:45:45.473
Great is your faithfulness to us, O God.

01:45:46.296 --> 01:45:51.795
The anointing is so strong, I don't know where to take it.

01:46:06.769 --> 01:46:07.119
I see the sun.

01:46:08.139 --> 01:46:10.150
I see the sun as the moon.

01:46:10.150 --> 01:46:13.463
Nothing in this life can survive without the sun.

01:46:13.463 --> 01:46:14.034
Nothing.

01:46:14.034 --> 01:46:19.200
As it is in the natural, so it is in the spiritual.

01:46:19.200 --> 01:46:22.409
Nothing can survive without the sun.

01:46:22.409 --> 01:46:24.452
Every living thing needs a sun.

01:46:25.333 --> 01:46:25.626
You understand?

01:46:25.626 --> 01:46:27.394
Like life, it brings life.

01:46:27.394 --> 01:46:30.213
Every living thing, we all need the sun.

01:46:30.213 --> 01:46:33.615
Every one of us, boy or girl, it doesn't matter.

01:46:33.615 --> 01:46:34.764
We all need this Jesus.

01:46:34.764 --> 01:46:43.146
I see the sun, and the sun was making all the flowers and everything grow as he was passing by.

01:46:43.146 --> 01:46:45.439
Everything is looking at the sun.

01:46:55.520 --> 01:46:55.840
The flowers, they all point toward the sun.

01:46:55.840 --> 01:46:58.260
The trees grow toward the light.

01:46:58.260 --> 01:46:59.340
We grow toward the light.

01:46:59.340 --> 01:47:05.910
But the Lord is bringing forth a new rain to make things grow, for we all just need a new drink.

01:47:05.910 --> 01:47:08.460
We cry unto thee, O Lord.

01:47:08.460 --> 01:47:10.440
We cry each day.

01:47:10.440 --> 01:47:13.429
We cry out to you each day.

01:47:13.429 --> 01:47:23.462
His desire for you is to come up underneath the greater flow of Him and the greater manifestations of the glory on you.

01:47:23.462 --> 01:47:29.920
There's much more for you as you go up and you know your authority.

01:47:29.920 --> 01:47:31.999
You must know your authority.

01:47:31.999 --> 01:47:43.531
But as of this night, see, it's time for you to come up and see the glorious way that I have for thee.

01:47:43.531 --> 01:47:45.679
Partake and stay.

01:47:47.670 --> 01:47:50.159
He wants you to come and stay.

01:47:50.159 --> 01:48:02.586
Stay open, for the greater days of the glory are upon you.

01:48:02.586 --> 01:48:12.098
For many have lost their way, but as of this day, they're finding their way—going back to the first love, going back to what you had before.

01:48:22.034 --> 01:48:22.468
You will see 'church unusual.

01:48:22.468 --> 01:48:37.439
' If you will operate in what I've called you to do—He's calling the church to operate as one, as it was in the book of Acts.

01:48:37.439 --> 01:48:39.724
They were of one sound and one accord.

01:48:39.724 --> 01:48:52.560
They become one sound and one accord when you move as one, flowing with the Son, flowing in the greater gift, flowing in this way each and every single day; there's nothing that you won't accomplish.

01:48:52.560 --> 01:49:05.733
When we pray and obey each and every single day, praying and obeying what the Spirit of the Lord tells you to do, coming up higher in the fire.

01:49:05.733 --> 01:49:14.102
Out of that belly shall flow the rivers of living water, flowing with the Holy Ghost and power.

01:49:14.102 --> 01:49:16.039
There's nothing you can't do.

01:49:18.730 --> 01:49:21.484
The greater works you will do as you go unto the Father.

01:49:29.250 --> 01:49:29.600
You are sitting at His feet, beneath that throne.

01:49:29.600 --> 01:49:33.040
Oh God, thank You.

01:49:33.040 --> 01:49:36.057
I'm just Your son, I'm just Your daughter.

01:49:36.057 --> 01:49:40.540
We're so hungry and thirsty; we just want to know You more.

01:49:40.540 --> 01:49:44.709
We want to have revelation knowledge of who You are.

01:49:44.709 --> 01:49:50.000
Thank You, Lord, that according to Ephesians, the eyes of our understanding would be enlightened.

01:49:50.000 --> 01:49:56.495
Father, I thank You that the enlightenment of my eyes allows me to know who I am in Christ.

01:49:56.495 --> 01:49:57.485
I know my authority.

01:49:57.485 --> 01:50:04.039
I know that I walk in abundance and the fruit of the Spirit.

01:50:04.039 --> 01:50:08.853
I'm walking in love, for faith works by love.

01:50:08.853 --> 01:50:10.906
Love never fails.

01:50:10.906 --> 01:50:14.700
Love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

01:50:14.700 --> 01:50:17.879
Love bears up under anything and everything.

01:50:19.152 --> 01:50:20.857
The foundation is love—that's 1 Corinthians 13.

01:50:20.857 --> 01:50:24.667
For You are the Most High; may You be glorified.

01:50:28.720 --> 01:50:28.960
We glorify You, O God.

01:50:28.960 --> 01:50:31.943
We magnify the King of kings and the Lord of lords.

01:50:31.943 --> 01:50:37.800
For Father, You said, 'If I be lifted up, I'll draw all men unto me.

01:50:37.800 --> 01:50:42.800
' Well, it's time to get out the bigger nets.

01:50:49.519 --> 01:50:55.760
We call in the unsaved from the north, south, east, and west, drawing them in in the name of Jesus.

01:51:00.000 --> 01:51:00.720
We call in the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

01:51:00.720 --> 01:51:05.740
Father, I thank You that it would be groundbreaking.

01:51:05.740 --> 01:51:08.293
We call in a more than five-billion-soul harvest.

01:51:08.293 --> 01:51:11.199
We're calling them all in right now, believing for big.

01:51:11.519 --> 01:51:14.151
You said, 'I wish that none should perish.

01:51:14.151 --> 01:51:16.114
' We call them in right now.

01:51:16.114 --> 01:51:19.000
We command Satan to release them right now.

01:51:19.000 --> 01:51:23.020
We call the eyes of their understanding to be enlightened and flooded with light.

01:51:23.020 --> 01:51:30.011
We call for the blinders to come off their eyes, for Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever.

01:51:30.011 --> 01:51:33.616
We say their eyes are open and full of light.

01:52:02.140 --> 01:52:02.490
We call for the salt to draw them in.

01:52:02.490 --> 01:52:06.130
Father, we won't lose our saltiness; we're salty for Jesus.

01:52:06.130 --> 01:52:12.570
For it is the salt that causes man to thirst, and we are the salt of the earth.

01:52:12.570 --> 01:52:21.173
We thank You, Lord, that we won't lose our saltiness and that people see the glory on us.

01:52:21.173 --> 01:52:31.199
Let every cell, every fiber, everything about us display the glory of God so that when people see us, they see Jesus.

01:52:31.199 --> 01:52:45.897
Everything that is holding us back or blocking us from being in the greater glory, Father, I thank You that You remove it.

01:52:45.897 --> 01:52:55.395
Thank You, Lord, that we're coming up higher with the fire, for the manifested presence of the glory of God, healings, and demonstrations of the glory.

01:52:55.395 --> 01:53:00.671
Thank You, Father, that we're always in the right place at the right time.

01:53:00.671 --> 01:53:03.499
We give You all the glory, honor, and praise.

01:53:03.499 --> 01:53:08.960
Father, you said there's going to be a shaking to awaken in the body of Christ.

01:53:21.669 --> 01:53:22.023
I thank You, Lord, that there's a rising up of new Davids who have a backbone like a crowbar.

01:53:22.023 --> 01:53:27.520
They rise up and do what You've called them to do with great power and authority.

01:53:33.919 --> 01:53:34.319
We don't shrink back; we keep pressing.

01:53:34.319 --> 01:53:43.920
Father, I thank You that we have authenticity in the body of Christ—that people are authentic and we get rid of this fakeness.

01:53:43.920 --> 01:53:49.760
A shaking in the church, Father, that we see authentic believers who practice what they preach.

01:53:49.760 --> 01:53:55.120
They act the way they need to act behind closed doors.

01:53:55.120 --> 01:54:06.159
If they mess up, they repent and turn before they burn.

01:54:06.159 --> 01:54:12.470
Get radical for Jesus.

01:54:22.959 --> 01:54:23.199
You can mess up and have a bad moment, but that doesn't mean you're a bad person.

01:54:27.840 --> 01:54:28.560
You just don't live in the moment.

01:54:33.866 --> 01:54:35.337
You keep on keeping on, seeking Him daily, Lord, and You said we'd find You.

01:54:35.337 --> 01:54:38.057
Knock and the door will be opened.

01:54:38.057 --> 01:54:40.034
Father, we seek You.

01:54:51.820 --> 01:54:52.120
We call for revival in Living Word and in these churches represented all around.

01:55:01.350 --> 01:55:01.540
We call for protection over President Trump and revival in the White House.

01:55:01.540 --> 01:55:05.902
We call for revival in South Korea, North Korea, China, and the underground church.

01:55:05.902 --> 01:55:07.467
We call for revival in Iran.

01:55:07.467 --> 01:55:14.011
We say in the name of Jesus, the persecution in Nigeria stops.

01:55:14.011 --> 01:55:19.119
Father, I thank You that the body of Christ rises up and the genocide stops in the name of Jesus.

01:55:28.680 --> 01:55:28.909
That the angels of the Lord would manifest and make war against it.

01:55:35.520 --> 01:55:35.787
That they would stand in there and say, 'There are more who are with us than there are with them.

01:55:38.033 --> 01:55:39.889
There are more who are with us than there are with them.

01:55:39.889 --> 01:56:00.914
' And I thank you that you, the God who has never changed, the God who is still the same, the same yesterday, today, and forever, warred on behalf of the people of the Bible, and he will war on behalf of the people of this world right now in Nigeria.

01:56:00.914 --> 01:56:10.560
Our brothers and sisters who are being slaughtered, I thank you, Lord, that it stops.

01:56:10.560 --> 01:56:16.559
I put a hedge, Father, with angelic aid and assistance all around them.

01:56:16.559 --> 01:56:19.640
Angelic aid and assistance all around the people of Nigeria.

01:56:19.640 --> 01:56:22.690
Angelic aid and assistance in the name of Jesus.

01:56:22.960 --> 01:56:41.199
We call angelic aid and assistance in the name of Jesus over the people of Nigeria and over Africa, wherever else this is happening, that the angels of the Lord, twelve-foot-tall angels with massive swords, are seen, and they go, 'We've got to get out of here!

01:56:41.199 --> 01:56:42.960
' and they are scared spitless.

01:56:42.960 --> 01:56:47.303
They will come out against us one way and flee before us seven ways.

01:56:52.640 --> 01:56:52.960
This stops, and the people of Nigeria are protected.

01:56:52.960 --> 01:56:56.533
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we see a turnaround.

01:56:56.533 --> 01:57:02.140
As of this day, we see a turnaround, and great revival breaks out in Nigeria.

01:57:02.140 --> 01:57:12.286
We call revival to break out all over Africa in the name of Jesus, from the top to the bottom, all around the sides.

01:57:12.286 --> 01:57:25.460
We call a major revival over the continent of Africa in the name of Jesus, for a major move of God is coming to the continent of Africa in the name of Jesus.

