Father, I thank you, Lord, that the major harvest of souls is coming over these nations in the name of Jesus; that a great shaking to awaken will manifest and shake the governments, shake the parliaments, shake the prime ministers, the governors, and all the people who are in authority.

01:57:55.439 --> 01:58:15.580
We call a great move of God over these nations in the name of Jesus, and that the greatest outpouring of the Spirit of God would be upon us in the name of Jesus with the greatest harvest of souls in the name of Jesus.

01:58:15.580 --> 01:58:16.624
We're calling them in.

01:58:16.624 --> 01:58:21.893
We're calling them in in the name of Jesus, that every one of them will get born again.

01:58:21.893 --> 01:58:23.520
We call a shaking.

01:58:37.310 --> 01:58:37.700
We call a shaking in the nations.

01:58:37.700 --> 01:58:39.646
We call a shaking and revival.

01:58:39.646 --> 01:58:43.671
We call revival a stirring in our hearts, a stirring of the lackadaisical.

01:58:43.671 --> 01:58:47.440
We call a stirring in them in the name of Jesus.

01:58:47.440 --> 01:58:58.452
All over Australia, we call a stirring in them, a stirring in them with great sounds of new worship, great sounds of new praise flowing out of our churches like we've never heard before.

01:59:02.239 --> 01:59:02.444
A great move of God in the name of Jesus.

01:59:02.444 --> 01:59:03.466
We're calling it in.

01:59:03.466 --> 01:59:05.760
We're calling it in in Jesus' name.

01:59:05.760 --> 01:59:11.493
Oh, come on, Father, that you would visit us one more time, one more major harvest time.

01:59:20.960 --> 01:59:21.383
We call a major move of God in the name of Jesus.

01:59:21.383 --> 01:59:23.074
Thank you, Lord.

01:59:34.540 --> 01:59:34.710
I know you've not forgotten us.

01:59:34.710 --> 01:59:39.831
Father, you said you'd never leave us and you'd never forsake us.

01:59:39.831 --> 01:59:44.200
We become bolder about who we are.

01:59:44.200 --> 01:59:45.227
Revival starts with us.

01:59:45.227 --> 01:59:47.220
Revival starts with you and me.

01:59:47.220 --> 01:59:48.610
Revival starts in our churches.

01:59:48.610 --> 01:59:50.868
He's looking; he's waiting on us.

01:59:50.868 --> 01:59:52.765
What would we do with it?

01:59:52.765 --> 02:00:00.700
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you stir in the people whatever it takes, that we have a 'whatever it takes' in these last days.

02:00:00.700 --> 02:00:01.799
We protect the unborn.

02:00:01.799 --> 02:00:03.377
We stand for the innocent.

02:00:03.377 --> 02:00:05.800
We stand for the unborn, the aborted babies.

